    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that presents like a car that has been carefully preserved or comprehensively sorted to a very high standard. The paint, trim, glass, and interior all show extremely well, with the kind of fit, finish, and cleanliness buyers hope to find but rarely do. It looks complete, properly cared for, and ready to be enjoyed immediately, whether you want a standout driver, a show-worthy weekend car, or a collector-quality addition to a garage. Expect a car that feels sharp, fresh, and unusually well kept throughout.",
