      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition car that shows well overall and should appeal to a buyer looking for a solid, well-kept driver. The body, paint, and trim present nicely with the expected minor cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle, and the interior appears tidy and cared for rather than freshly restored. It has the kind of condition that makes a strong impression in person without pretending to be perfect, and buyers should expect a respectable, enjoyable car with normal signs of age and use.",
