    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward value for a driver seeking affordable transportation. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who appreciates a lower entry price and the opportunity to own a dependable daily-use vehicle without overpaying. A practical choice for commuting, a backup car, or a project-minded buyer looking for solid value.",
