      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an inexpensive car with potential? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option that could be a great fit for someone handy, a first-time buyer, or anyone needing cheap wheels without spending a fortune. It\u2019s priced to reflect its condition and has plenty of life left for the right person. If you want a straightforward deal on an affordable car, come take a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
